item.description:

[quote=“Chassy13, post:6, topic:379929”][quote author=LilXCj link=topic=475771.msg3481048#msg3481048 date=1296128197]
I don’t like rap but I do have something about the same beat throughout an entire song. I listen to techno/dance/hardcore (whatever you want to call it these days) which is usually just several beats and one main chorus beat that is played through the majority of the song. I find it a preference because it doesn’t need lyrics to be a good song. I listen to other things as well.
[/quote]

I like certain types of techno, but I don’t listen to it often. Same beats over and over bore me, which is the reason I like Metal; it has different beats added in with lyrics. Metal owns. As for the same beat over and over, I hate it. My brother listens to CD’s while he sleeps. Really annoying.
